headline: Hardware & Infrastructure Stocks Q4 Recap: Benchmarking Dell (NYSE:DELL)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Dell (NYSE:DELL) and the best and worst performers in the hardware & infrastructure industry.

headline: Which AI Stock Is Cheaper: Dell or Super Micro Computer?
summary: Dell (NYSE: DELL) and Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ: SMCI) are leading players in the artificial intelligence (AI) server space.  Comparing a company's expected annual earnings per share against its stock price is one way to get a look at a stock's valuation profile, and a smaller earnings ratio can potentially indicate that a company is generating stronger profit relative to its valuation.  The following chart provides a comparison of the two companies' valuations by forward price-to-earnings ratios.
